Tumor growth data for a melanoma cancer model (A375)

Source: R/data.r
melanoma1.Rd

The A375 cell line (metastatic melanoma) was used to create CDX (Cell Line Derived Xenograft) mice.

Usage

melanoma1

Format

A data frame with 600 rows and 4 variables:

ID

Mouse identifier to indicate repeated measurements on the same mouse. (factor)

Day

Day of measurment (integer)

Volume

Tumor volume (double)

Treatment

Treatment group (factor). A = control, B = Vemurafenib (BRAF inhibitor), C = Buthionine sulfoximine (BSO), D = Vemurafenib + BSO.

Source

University of Iowa, Holden Cancer Center, experiment SLB19-022.
